      "id": "69ec192a0000000000d5afb3",
      "text": " [vlzs 2026/04/25 書いてて自分でよくわからなくなったやつ]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777080618,
      "updated": 1777101106
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec19660000000000d5afcc",
      "text": " 有酸素運動をしたあとはタイピングがとても早い",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777080679,
      "updated": 1777105950
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec7c0f0000000000c756ae",
      "text": "  つまづかなくて嬉しい",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777105935,
      "updated": 1777106091
    },
    {
      "id": "69ed0b61000000000070f323",
      "text": " 入眠に失敗したので井戸端に来た",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777142626,
      "updated": 1777142647
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec7bfb0000000000c756ad",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777105915,
      "updated": 1777105915
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec20420000000000b003e5",
      "text": "[suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777082435,
      "updated": 1777082437
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec20450000000000b003e7",
      "text": " 刺激が強いというか、過激なページの閲覧用に、フィルターとして「[閲覧注意]」というページ（アイコン）をつくりました",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777082437,
      "updated": 1777103525
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec206c0000000000b003ee",
      "text": "  [閲覧注意.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777082476,
      "updated": 1777082491
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec20560000000000b003e8",
      "text": " 「見るなら注意して見てね」という[注意喚起]を目的にしています",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777082454,
      "updated": 1777083070
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec20800000000000b003ef",
      "text": "  [フィルターは各自がやればいい]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777082497,
      "updated": 1777082516
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec20560000000000b003e9",
      "text": " それで、みなさんにお聞きしたいことがあるのですが、閲覧注意の画像の派手さはこれくらいでいいですか？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777082454,
      "updated": 1777082459
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec20560000000000b003ea",
      "text": " 派手にすれば、どぎつすぎて、見るだけでストレスになりますし",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777082454,
      "updated": 1777082459
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec20560000000000b003eb",
      "text": " 地味にすれば、注意喚起の役割がきかなくなります",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777082454,
      "updated": 1777082459
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec20560000000000b003ec",
      "text": " 丁度良い加減が知りたい",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777082454,
      "updated": 1777082459
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec20560000000000b003ed",
      "text": " ご意見ください",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777082454,
      "updated": 1777082459
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec2d9800000000002fe18d",
      "text": " [/ [ネタバレ注意.icon]]このくらいが良さげ[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777085848,
      "updated": 1777085869
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec38c9000000000001971e",
      "text": "   これはgeminiが作ったネタバレ防止画像[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777088714,
      "updated": 1777088730
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec31db00000000002fe18e",
      "text": "  [https://gyazo.com/fc44a8e3f25a058d38c19d13b08d9d95]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777086939,
      "updated": 1777086947
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec31e300000000002fe18f",
      "text": "   自然物：柔らかい・どぎつくない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777086947,
      "updated": 1777086990
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec320e00000000002fe190",
      "text": "   火：危険",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777086990,
      "updated": 1777087004
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec332500000000008ee328",
      "text": "    [** [閲覧注意.icon]] ちょっと文字が読みにくくないですか？[suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777087270,
      "updated": 1777087355
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec395a00000000007798d5",
      "text": "   縦横比とフォントをもうちょっと変えてみようかな[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777088858,
      "updated": 1777089030
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec39880000000000f6eadf",
      "text": "   　たぶん、[閲覧注意]のページに直接画像を貼ったほうが話がはやいですよ [suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777088904,
      "updated": 1777088955
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec3cc400000000002a5b9c",
      "text": "   　 フォント色を白にするか、白抜き文字にはできませんか？ [suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777089732,
      "updated": 1777089781
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec3ea10000000000df7979",
      "text": "   　 [\" フォント色を白]それ見づらいよ[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777090209,
      "updated": 1777090352
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec3ea60000000000df797a",
      "text": "    　 [https://gyazo.com/051ce18a4f4d7edb27f66ce7d9153920]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777090214,
      "updated": 1777090217
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec3ea90000000000df797b",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t[\" 白抜き]こっちは見やすくはなったけど、注意を引きすぎる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777090217,
      "updated": 1777090620
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec3ef00000000000df797d",
      "text": " \t\t\t\t\t[https://gyazo.com/44f6e2ad821555959af74850d56a95a3]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777090288,
      "updated": 1777090289
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec3eec0000000000df797c",
      "text": "  2026/04/25 16:10:50 [suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777090284,
      "updated": 1777101176
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec6906000000000092d757",
      "text": "   現状の閲覧注意のアイコンで問題ないでしょうか？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777101062,
      "updated": 1777101118
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec693e000000000092d758",
      "text": "   特に異論がなければ、このままでいこうと思います",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777101118,
      "updated": 1777101171
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec697e000000000092d759",
      "text": "   （変更も簡単だし）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777101182,
      "updated": 1777101200
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec275a0000000000dbc05e",
      "text": " >[https://x.com/kno32/status/2047834402198298989 @kno32]: GPT Images 2おもしろいね",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777084251,
      "updated": 1777113886
    },
